<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/7(Sat.)Can a drug make you tell the truth?/3 Ways to Make Better Decisions –By Thinking Like a Computer: Tom Griffiths]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=314&amp;p=330#p330"><![CDATA[
9/7(Sat.) Can a drug make you tell the truth?/3 Ways to Make Better Decisions – By Thinking Like a Computer: Tom Griffiths (Host:Kelvin)<br /><br />Article 1: Can a drug make you tell the truth?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-24371140">https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-24371140</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1,Will you agree or not,If government pass the laws that everyone can buy this &quot;tell the truth drug &quot;?<br />2,Are you good at lying or good at detecting lying?<br />3,when you ask someone a favor,but if the answer is no.you prefer they lie to you   or tell you the true reason.<br /><br /><br />Article 2: 3 Ways to Make Better Decisions – By Thinking Like a Computer: Tom Griffiths (Transcript)<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://singjupost.com/3-ways-to-make-better-decisions-by-thinking-like-a-computer-tom-griffiths-transcript/">https://singjupost.com/3-ways-to-make-b ... ranscript/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1,Do you make a decision easily?sometimes it's difficult to make a decision.<br />2,When you have to make a difficult decision,how Will you deal with it?<br />3,After this gathering, what did you get from this article?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk <br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion <br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences <br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<br /><br />Royal 三峽 , Royal new branch information, <br />Every Monday evening: 8:00pm- 10pm:  摩斯漢堡  北大特區 土城區學成路712號, next to the park. <br />Please keep contact with President Ophelia.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Mon Sep 02, 2019 12:46 pm</p><hr />
